snippet.title: Amber Heard DESTROYED On The Stand As JOHNNY DEPP's Lawyer PROVES she LIED!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard took the stand again and was destroyed by Johnny Depp's lawyers as they proved that Amber Heard lied!!

Support Johnny Depp through this trial, i believe he is innocent and Amber Heard is the one guilty of abusing him.

A photo of Amber Heard with Johnny Depp and Rolling Stones guitarist Keith Richards was submitted to a London court on Tuesday – to try to prove the actress was lying about a supposed beating she got from the actor.

“Do you agree that there is absolutely no injury on your face in this photo?” Depp’s lawyer, Eleanor Laws, asked Heard – who was on the witness stand for her second straight day of testimony in Depp’s sensational libel case against a British tabloid.
